units metal
boundary p p p
atom_style atomic
read_data carbon.data
neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify every 1

pair_style tersoff
pair_coeff * * C_2010.tersoff C

thermo     1
thermo_style custom step pe
thermo_modify flush yes
dump dump1 all custom 1 dump.xyz element x y z
dump_modify dump1 element C
minimize 1.0e-10 1.0e-13 10000 100000
